A detachment of men of the Nigeria Police Force (NPF) have arrived the national secretariat of the All Progressives Congress (APC) to ostensibly to forestall any breakdown of law and order. LEADERSHIP observed that a total of 9 trucks full of well-armed police men are at the APC secretariat with some are  roaming around the compound,  asking staff to return to their offices. As at the time of filing this report, it was yet to ascertain who called for the reinforcement. A source however said that thugs were seen gathering near the party office hence the move to bridge any security laps. More Details Later …